{{Year in Burundi|1993}}

The following lists events that happened during '''[[1993]] in [[Burundi]]'''.

==Events==
===October===
* October 21 - President [[Melchior Ndadaye|Ndadaye]] was assassinated by [[Tutsi]] extremists, starting [[Burundian Genocide|another genocide]] against Tutsis and a [[Burundian Civil War|civil war]].<ref name=Notholt2.26>[[#Notholt|Notholt (2008)]], p. [https://books.google.com/books?id=E7cNWmXFrNMC&pg=SA2-PA26 2.26]</ref>

