{{Infobox airport | name = N'Délé Airport | IATA = NDL | ICAO = FEFN | type = Public | city-served = [[N'Délé]], [[Central African Republic]] | location = | owner = | elevation-f = 1677 | elevation-m = | coordinates = {{coord|8|25|35|N|20|38|07|E|region:CF_type:airport|name=N'Délé Airport (N'Délé)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Central African Republic | pushpin_label= '''NDL''' | pushpin_map_caption = Location of N'Délé Airport in the Central African Republic | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = 17/35 | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = 1509 | r1-surface = Grass | footnotes = Source: Landings.com<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?FEFN Airport record for N'Délé Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-08-26</ref> Google Maps<ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=8.42688888888889,20.6352222222222+%28N'Délé+Airport%29|title=location of N'Délé Airport|accessdate=2013-08-26}}</ref> GCM<ref>{{GCM|NDL|N'Délé Airport}}</ref> }}
'''N'Délé Airport''' {{Airport codes|NDL|FEFN}} is an airport serving [[N'Délé]], a town in the [[Bamingui-Bangoran]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. The airport is on the northwest edge of the town.
The Ndele [[VHF omnidirectional range|VOR]] (Ident: '''LE''')is located {{convert|3.5|nmi|km|1}} east-southeast of the airport.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ourairports.com/navaids/LE/Ndele_VOR_CF/|title=Ndele VOR (LE) @ OurAirports|website=ourairports.com|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
