'''Natakhtari Airfield''' {{Airport codes||UGSA}} is an domestic [[airport]] located in [[Natakhtari]], [[Mtskheta-Mtianeti]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]. It also serves [[Mtskheta]] and [[Tbilisi]]. It only serves domestic flights. A bus links the airfield with [[Tbilisi]].
