'''University of Mindelo''' ({{lang-pt|Universidade do Mindelo}}) is an institute of higher education in the city of [[Mindelo]], island of [[São Vicente, Cape Verde|São Vicente]], [[Cape Verde]]. It was established in 2002, and officially started operations on June 9, 2003 as the ''Instituto de Estudos Superiores Isidoro da Graça''. It was converted into the University of Mindelo in 2010.<ref>[https://uni-mindelo.edu.cv/pt/reitoria/54-reitor-um O Reitor da Universidade do Mindelo], University of Mindelo {{pt icon}}</ref>

